---
// Scene 2: The empathy hook — we understand your problem
---

<section class="py-24 md:py-36 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Subtle background texture -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.02]" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 1px 1px, var(--color-text) 1px, transparent 0); background-size: 24px 24px;"></div>

  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 lg:px-6">
    <!-- The big question -->
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-20">
      <h2 data-reveal class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold text-text leading-[1.1] tracking-tight">
        Du har en bedrift å drive.
      </h2>
      <h2 data-reveal class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold text-text-light leading-[1.1] tracking-tight mt-2">
        Ikke et klesskap å fylle.
      </h2>
      <p data-reveal class="mt-8 text-xl md:text-2xl text-text-secondary leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto font-light">
        Å finne riktig arbeidstøy, få logoen på plass, sørge for at alt matcher — det tar tid du ikke har. <strong class="text-text font-semibold">Vi tar den jobben.</strong>
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Three pain points → solutions -->
    <div data-reveal-stagger class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 lg:gap-8">
      <!-- Pain 1 -->
      <div class="group relative">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl border border-border p-8 h-full transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1">
          <!-- Problem indicator -->
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-red-50 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M21 21l-5.197-5.197m0 0A7.5 7.5 0 105.196 15.803a7.5 7.5 0 0010.607 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-red-400 uppercase tracking-wider">Problemet</span>
          </div>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-text mb-3">Uoversiktlig marked</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Hundrevis av leverandører, tusenvis av produkter. Hvem leverer faktisk kvalitet? Hvem kan du stole på?
          </p>

          <!-- Solution -->
          <div class="pt-5 border-t border-border">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
              <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-accent">Vår løsning</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">6 nøye utvalgte merkevarer, én kontaktperson som kjenner deg.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Pain 2 -->
      <div class="group relative">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl border border-border p-8 h-full transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-red-50 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M9.53 16.122a3 3 0 00-5.78 1.128 2.25 2.25 0 01-2.4 2.245 4.5 4.5 0 008.4-2.245c0-.399-.078-.78-.22-1.128zm0 0a15.998 15.998 0 003.388-1.62m-5.043-.025a15.994 15.994 0 011.622-3.395m3.42 3.42a15.995 15.995 0 004.764-4.648l3.876-5.814a1.151 1.151 0 00-1.597-1.597L14.146 6.32a15.996 15.996 0 00-4.649 4.764m3.42 3.42a6.776 6.776 0 00-3.42-3.42" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-red-400 uppercase tracking-wider">Problemet</span>
          </div>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-text mb-3">For mange ledd</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Én for klær, en for trykk, en tredje for design. Koordinering, tre fakturaer, ingenting matcher.
          </p>

          <div class="pt-5 border-t border-border">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
              <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-accent">Vår løsning</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">Klær + trykk + design = én leveranse, én faktura.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Pain 3 -->
      <div class="group relative">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl border border-border p-8 h-full transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-red-50 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M8.25 18.75a1.5 1.5 0 01-3 0m3 0a1.5 1.5 0 00-3 0m3 0h6m-9 0H3.375a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V14.25m17.25 4.5a1.5 1.5 0 01-3 0m3 0a1.5 1.5 0 00-3 0m3 0h1.125c.621 0 1.129-.504 1.09-1.124a17.902 17.902 0 00-3.213-9.193 2.056 2.056 0 00-1.58-.86H14.25M16.5 18.75h-2.25m0-11.177v-.958c0-.568-.422-1.048-.987-1.106a48.554 48.554 0 00-10.026 0 1.106 1.106 0 00-.987 1.106v7.635m12-6.677v6.677m0 4.5v-4.5m0 0h-12" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-red-400 uppercase tracking-wider">Problemet</span>
          </div>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-text mb-3">Profilen stopper ved klærne</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Biler, vinduer, bannere, skilt — alt skal henge sammen med resten av profilen din. Det gjør det sjelden.
          </p>

          <div class="pt-5 border-t border-border">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
              <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-accent">Vår løsning</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">Foliering, storformat og fasadeskilt — same designer, same fargeprofil.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
